{"word":"ἄνωθεν","slug":"ἄνωθεν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἄνωϑεν</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄνω\">ἄνω</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp> <i>from above</i></b> (sometimes reinforced by <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπό\">ἀπό</a></el> or <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκ\">ἐκ</a></el>): of fabric <i>from (the) top</i> <b><a href='B:470 27:51'>Mt 27:51</a>; <a href='B:480 15:38'>Mk 15:38</a>; <a href='B:500 19:23'>J 19:23</a>;</b> of heaven/God <b><a href='B:500 3:31'>J 3:31</a>; <a href='B:500 19:11'>19:11</a>; <a href='B:660 1:17'>Js 1:17</a>; <a href='B:660 3:15'>3:15</a>, <a href='B:660 3:17'>17</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp> <i>from the beginning,</i></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on scope of treatment <b><a href='B:490 1:3'>Lk 1:3</a>; <i>from the first</i></b><i></i> or <b><i>for a long time</i></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on a period of time for acquaintance <b><a href='B:510 26:5'>Ac 26:5</a>; <a href='B:550 4:9'>Gal 4:9</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp> <i>again</i> <a href='B:500 3:3'>J 3:3</a>, <a href='B:500 3:7'>7</a>,</b> interpreted indirectly through <el>δεύτερον</el> in 3:4, but <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πάλιν\">πάλιν</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄνωθεν\">ἄνωθεν</a></el> conveys the sense <i>all over again.</i> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνώγαιον/ἀνώγεον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνωτερικός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}